content:
Admins can clone a bot quickly to help with development, or they can create a similar bot for a different use case.

Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein Bots is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions


To build and manage Einstein Bots:

Customize Application

OR

Modify Metadata

OR

Manage Bots

Navigate to the Bot Setup Page and find the bot in the My Bots list.
Click the dropdown  and select Clone.
Enter a new Bot Display Name and API name. The bot requires a unique Bot Display Name and API Name for the cloned bot.
After you save your work, the Bot Builder opens to the new bot.
title: Cloning Einstein Bots in Salesforce Service Cloud
